    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of 31 barrels of fuel stashed in Kilinochchi - one arrested",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kilinochchi police have said that 31 barrels containing diesel, kerosene and petrol were recovered in Anmitha Navapuram area of \u200b\u200bKilinochchi city.",
        "Today (03-07-2022) on the basis of special information received by the police regarding the illegal storage of fuel in Kilinochchi city, the police conducted a sudden round-up and recovered 31 pellets of diesel, kerosene and petrol hidden in a house in the said area and the suspect has been arrested."
      ],
